data.title: Ocean Minded™ Premium Collection
data.description: Our collaborative relationship with The Sandalman, of Newport Beach, CA combines the best of both companies by taking Ocean Minded's original Makena and Mokulua sandals and updating them here in the 'Golden State' with premium materials using The Sandalman's handcrafted techniques.

data.title: Ocean Minded™ Back To Our Roots Collection
data.description: The Ocean Minded™ Back To Our Roots Collection is just that, a renewed focus on the core styles that maintain the heritage of our brand. For 2014 we take our iconic styles and update them using luxe trends, ornamentation, texture, new materials and color freshness. We also update classic silhouettes, look back into our archives and reintroduce original styles that bring the past into the future.

data.title: Ocean Minded™ Croslite™ Collection
data.description:
Many or our Ocean Minded™ footwear styles feature Croslite™ material -- a proprietary, revolutionary technology that gives each pair the soft, comfortable, lightweight and odor-resistant qualities our customers have come to love and expect.

Additionally, Croslite™ material is non-marking, easy to clean, and forms to your foot for all-day comfort, providing us with a key point of differentiation in the marketplace.
